imdb.plot outline: Michelle Phan and Kylie Jenner might be the tops makeup gurus (or at least the most popular) but do they get YOUR mood?. Megan understands your mood and is here to show you how to make your face show it. Weekly comedy series on YouTube channel "Hissy Fit" that parodies the typical makeup vlogger format. Written, directed, edited, animated and performed by Megan Toenyes.
